word_mean_info__list.difference: 普通用词，美国英语多用。指某事也许如此，含不能确定意味。
指客观上潜存着发生某种变化的可能。
一般指根据逻辑推理，估计有发生的可能，把握性较大，语气比possibly强。

bilingual.target: 也许我是一个古怪的人。

bilingual.source: Possibly not, but we have to be careful.
bilingual.target: 也许不会，但我们必须万分小心。

bilingual.source: Quite possibly, and we might lower it accordingly.
bilingual.target: 很可能如此，我们也许会据此降低盗贼的伤害。

bilingual.source: We could expect entertainment about dawn, possibly earlier.
bilingual.target: 等到天亮前后, 也许还到不了那时候,我们就可以有个开心取乐的机会了.

bilingual.source: Could it possibly be that he might be that ere the day was done!
bilingual.target: 天黑以前，也许他也会变成这个样子！

bilingual.source: Possibly she really does not belong to me, I should give …
bilingual.target: 也许她真的不属于我，我应该放弃，顺其自然。

bilingual.source: It's possible you have heard many of these, and possibly not. So, let's make sure that you know all of them. Okay.
bilingual.target: 也许其中一些词，你之前听说过，也许没听过。就让我们一起来学习这些词吧。

bilingual.source: We couldn't possibly know what we wanted if we hadn't agreed first.
bilingual.target: 如果事先不商量商量，我们也许连彼此想要些什么都不知道。

bilingual.source: Possibly most familiar is rhyme, the repetition of like sounds in word endings.
bilingual.target: 最常见的重复也许是韵脚，单词结尾的音节重复。

bilingual.source: I would possibly very like doing sports, and maybe I am good at basketball.
bilingual.target: 也许我们只离成功一步之遥，但是我们就是急躁了。

yingyinNormal.en: And possibly most damning of all, the police arrested someone else for this murder.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也许最糟糕的是，警察曾逮捕过另一名嫌犯。

yingyinNormal.en: Perhaps I can contact you, possibly through my poetry falcon. Poetry falcon. I like that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也许我可以透过我的诗鹰联系你。诗鹰，我喜欢。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm hearing now that the president received at least one gunshot to the abdomen, possibly more, that he clutched his stomach, that he fell instantly to the ground, and there were screams, people panicking, that it has been very chaotic at that scene.
yingyinNormal.zh: 导播现在告诉我总统至少腹部中了一枪，也许不止，他紧捂腹部，立即倒地，现场尖叫连连，人群陷入恐慌，场面十分混乱。

yingyinNormal.en: I couldn't possibly. Why not?
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么可以呢？为什么不行?

yingyinNormal.en: Or possibly Durham, Noh Carolina.
yingyinNormal.zh: 或者在北卡罗来纳的杜伦。

yingyinNormal.en: How can you possibly lose? Like this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么可能输呢？像这样。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you just making this up? Possibly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是你编出来的吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I can't do that. I couldn't possibly do that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不能这么做，我不可能这么做。

yingyinNormal.en: This can't possibly... I can't, can't. I can't...
yingyinNormal.zh: 这不可能... 我不能，不能，我不能...

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, please, how could I possibly devastate Howard?
yingyinNormal.zh: 请问，我怎么可能把霍华德弄崩溃？

yingyinNormal.en: You can't know that. How can you possibly know that?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么知道，你怎么可能知道？

yingyinNormal.en: Really? LeVar Burton's coming here? Possibly. I Tweeted him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真的吗？勒瓦尔·布尔顿也要来吗？可能，我在推特上联系他了。

yingyinNormal.en: Attlee. He couldn't possibly be talking about that "Syndicate"?
yingyinNormal.zh: 艾德礼，他说的不会是那个"辛迪加"吧？

yingyinNormal.en: I have a meeting after the game. You're going to the game? Yeah. Possibly. Possibly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 比赛后我有个会，你们也去看比赛? 是的，有可能。有可能。

yingyinNormal.en: All right, then go. Listen to you. How can I possibly go?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那就去呗。听听你说的话，我怎么去啊？

yingyinNormal.en: I just need to know, how could these possibly be collated?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想知道，这些债券是怎么过审的？

yingyinNormal.en: I owe her more than I can possibly fathom. And she owes me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我欠她太多，多到我无法想象。而她也欠我。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, with you around, how could I ever possibly get Lucas alone?
yingyinNormal.zh: 有你在这边晃悠，我怎么可能跟卢卡斯单独相处？

yingyinNormal.en: Sweetie, you can't possibly remember that. You were barely a year old.
yingyinNormal.zh: 宝贝，你不可能记得的，当时你还不满一岁。

yingyinNormal.en: We killed a lot, but we saved more lives than you can possibly imagine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们杀了很多人，但我们拯救的生命多得超乎你们的想象。
